SUMMARY:"A Sheep From Another Fold"- Spiritual Video Night
DESCRIPTION:Roanoke Spiritual Experiences Group\n**Description:**\nCome jo
 in us for a 30-minute video of timeless wisdom from Harold Klemp’s talk\
 , **“A Sheep From Another Fold.**” Uplifting and insightful\, his talk
 s can help you unravel some of the perplexing mysteries of life. Each show
 ing will be followed by group discussion\; a time to share your own experi
 ences and nagging questions about life’s many challenges.\nSponsored by 
 ECKANKAR\, the Path of Spiritual Freedom.\nPlease register in advance for 
 this meeting at:\n[https://us06web.zoom.us/meeting/register/DZQK4PUeSBmaxd
 eqEy_Hjw](https://us06web.zoom.us/meeting/register/DZQK4PUeSBmaxdeqEy_Hjw)
 \nAfter registering\, you will receive a confirmation email containing log
 in information for joining the meeting.\nINTERNATIONAL GUESTS\, PLEASE NOT
 E: This event is not intended for anyone who is barred by the laws of thei
 r country from attending. Please follow the laws of your home country.
